<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10437828>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Collected specimens (A–C), and distribution in southeastern Brazil and adjacent areas (D–F). Gerromorpha, Gerridae. A. Microvelia ayacuchana, apterous male from Iúna, Espírito Santo (−20.3613, −41.7309). B. Microvelia hamadae, apterous male from Bocaina de Minas, Minas Gerais (−22.2964, −44.5566). C. Microvelia hinei, apterous female from Conceição da Barra, Espírito Santo (−18.2692, −39.7814). Scale bars: 1 mm (A–B), 0.5 mm (C)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10437828/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

